                          Clear Blockages: If the drain hole is blocked, use a
                          small funnel to pour warm water into the drain or use
                          a hairdryer to melt any ice blocking the drain. Ensure
                          the water flows freely into the drain pan.
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </li>

